---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us | Maison Interiors">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex-1 w-full">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-foreground mb-8">Contact Us</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed">
      <p>At Maison Interiors, we value open dialogue with our readers, design professionals, and industry partners.</p>
      <p>Whether you have a question about one of our architectural guides, wish to propose an editorial partnership, or need to report a technical issue with our platform, our team is ready to assist you.</p>

      <section class="mt-8 p-6 bg-muted/20 rounded-sm border border-border">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-foreground mb-3">Editorial & General Inquiries</h2>
        <p>Please reach out to our team directly via email:</p>
        <a href="mailto:contact@maisoninteriorshome.com" class="text-primary font-medium underline mt-2 inline-block hover:text-foreground">contact@maisoninteriorshome.com</a>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm mt-8">We aim to respond to all legitimate inquiries within 24 to 48 business hours.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>